<title type="html"><![CDATA[Tagging and timing NSF music]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=1116&amp;p=9622#p9622"><![CDATA[
I'm starting this issue fresh; ignore previous discussion. My overall objective is to work with others on building an archive of timed and tagged NSF music. Let's first list whatever goals we have.<br /><br /><span style="text-decoration: underline">Goals</span><br />- Duration and title for each track of an NSF<br />- Time accuracy of at least 1/60 second<br />- Tagging tools work on any platform<br />- Easy to tag an NSF with automated timing<br />- Well-defined file format<br />- Playlist support<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=17">blargg</a> — Wed Feb 15, 2006 5:05 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
